                    <span>This is by far a strong emphasis on doing all the dirty work before making the big mistake of starting before you have anything to start with.  Its like the thumbnails before you paint.  They won't let you touch the flash before you know what, how, why's to create a cartoon.  Anyone after the film makers approach or interested in long term animating should have this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Guiding the way</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
                      /
                      <span>5</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
